* {{a|GenAm}} {{IPA|/ɪˈlɛktɹɑn/|lang=en}}
* {{audio|en-us-electron.ogg|Audio (US)|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{lb|en|particle}} The [[subatomic particle]] having a negative charge and orbiting the [[nucleus]]; the flow of electrons in a [[conductor]] constitutes [[electricity]].
# {{lb|en|chemistry|obsolete}} [[alloy|Alloys]] of [[magnesium]] and other metals, like [[aluminum]] or [[zinc]], that were manufactured by the German company Chemische Fabrik Griesheim-Elektron.

